title: Russia-Ukraine Invasion: Inside One Tech Company’s Attempt to Evacuate Employees - The Wall Street Journal
content: Russia-Ukraine Invasion: Inside One Tech Company’s Attempt to Evacuate Employees  The Wall Street Journal
description: Fractal Analytics, a New York-based artificial-intelligence company with 81 workers in Ukraine, set up some staff in western Ukraine, helped others leave the country entirely and offered to pay salaries in advance.
